graph LR
    subgraph Inputs
        X1[Input x₁]
        X2[Input x₂]
        X3[Input x₃]
        XN[Input xₙ]
    end

    subgraph Weights
        W1[Weight w₁]
        W2[Weight w₂]
        W3[Weight w₃]
        WN[Weight wₙ]
    end

    subgraph Computation
        SUM[Σ Weighted Sum + Bias]
        ACT[Activation Function<br/>f x ≥ 0 → 1<br/>f x < 0 → 0]
    end

    subgraph Output
        Y[Output ŷ<br/>0 or 1]
    end

    X1 --> |×| W1
    X2 --> |×| W2
    X3 --> |×| W3
    XN --> |×| WN

    W1 --> SUM
    W2 --> SUM
    W3 --> SUM
    WN --> SUM

    BIAS[Bias b] --> SUM

    SUM --> ACT
    ACT --> Y
